title: FUBAR Destroyer 2014 v2
description:
FUBAR Destroyer 2014 v2
-----------------------

Another version of this evil data-destroying tool!


This application has 1 purpose, and 1 purpose only:
It will permanently WIPE & DESTROY all files on all harddisks and removable disks!
Recovery will not be possible.

As always, you get 2 warnings when you try to run this application.


News in this version:
- Full native support for Vista/7/8. This version will not work on XP or older.
- Introducing "Aggressive Mode": This mode will launch several threads at once.
- Warnings have been updated.

When you run this application, you will be presented with the usual warning.
The second warning, is not a particular warning. It is a question to you, the user, if you want to use Aggressive Mode, and the last chance for you to cancel the application.



/Ubehage
